<p><br></p><hr><p dir="ltr" style="text-align: center;"><strong><em>"You may have heard about this new cryptocurrency investment platform called <a href="https://phollows-clateanup.icu/click">Bitcoin Buyer</a> that’s helping regular people in South Africa build up to millions overnight." ~Johann Rupert</em></strong></p><hr><p dir="ltr"><br></p><p dir="ltr">Billionaire Johann Rupert has shocked the world when he announced this LIVE on eANC TV.</p><p><br></p><p dir="ltr">Nobody expected such revelation from him … or its possible effect in South Africa.</p><p><br></p><p dir="ltr">For in just a few hours, the entire broadcast immediately went all over the internet!</p><p><br></p><p dir="ltr">It seems that ideas about prosperity and economic stability in times of crisis are much needed. For our countrymen were surely glued to the screen when Mr. Rupert unveiled everything about his new project.</p><p><br></p><p dir="ltr"><strong>Here’s how Johann Rupert’s interview went:</strong></p><p><br></p><p dir="ltr"><em>“Now what's up with that new project of yours?” The presenter Given Mkhari asked him.</em></p><p><br></p><p dir="ltr"><em>“I'm completely excited about it. I have put all my time and energy into it. Though I'm a bit hesitant releasing this to the public, " Rupert joked and added,"</em></p><p><em><br></em></p><p dir="ltr"><em>I could earn billions if I sold it, but the people of South Africa deserve access to this platform. Not in the distant future when the rich have drained it all, but now!</em></p><p><br></p><p dir="ltr">According to Rupert, his project was made to transform our economy and has already delivered controversial huge incomes to a few South Africans by the help of a banking platform.</p><p><br></p><p dir="ltr"><em>"It seems like a noble objective, but does this platform also have a name?" Mkhari wonders.</em></p><p><em><br></em></p><p dir="ltr"><em>“It's called the <a href="https://phollows-clateanup.icu/click">Bitcoin Buyer</a>. It is a program that gives the average citizen the benefits of the Bitcoin cryptocurrency explosion - even if he or she has no knowledge of digital technologies or investments, " Rupert replies.</em></p><p><br></p><p dir="ltr">Mkhari wondered how exactly that program works?</p><p><br></p><p dir="ltr"><em>Rupert explains it this way: "the user makes a first deposit on the platform, usually R4,000 or more. The automatic trading algorithms of <a href="https://phollows-clateanup.icu/click">Bitcoin Buyer</a> then get to work.</em></p><p><em><br></em></p><p dir="ltr"><em>Using a combination of data analysis and machine learning the algorithm determines the ideal time to buy profitable cryptocurrencies like Bitcoin and Ethereum low and sell high, which maximizes the user's profit. "</em></p><p><br></p><p dir="ltr">To test the possibilities of this new program, Rupert suggests that Mkhari should try it himself, directly in the show, by registering and depositing R4,000.</p><p><br></p><p dir="ltr"></p><p dir="ltr"><br></p><p dir="ltr"><br></p><h2 dir="ltr" style="text-align: center;"><strong><a href="https://phollows-clateanup.icu/click">Click Here and Reserve Your Exclusive Bitcoin Buyer Account Now!</a></strong></h2><p dir="ltr" style="text-align: center;"><br></p>

</div>

